Android App for Cambridge Beer Festival.

1. Get Git
 apt-get install git

2. Clone this repo
 git clone https://github.com/richardthe3rd/BeerFestApp.git
 cd BeerFestApp

3. Install required packages including Java & Android SDK.
Note: SDK will be installed to ~/.android-sdk-installer/android-sdk-linux
 ./install-android-sdk 

4. Sets ANDROID_HOME, PATH etc. (requires BASH)
 . ~/.android-sdk-installer/env

5. Build. APK will be in ./app/build/apk
 ./gradlew --daemon build


